DPA Amendment for EU, UK, and Swiss SCCs
In 2021, the European Commission and the Swiss Federal Data Protection and Information Commission issued new Standard Contractual Clauses ("2021 SCCs"). Additionally, in 2022, the UK Parliament approved the UK International Data Transfer Addendum to the EU SCCs (‚ÄúUK Addendum‚Äù). The 2021 SCCs and UK Addendum replace the Standard Contractual Clauses enacted in 2010 (‚Äú2010 SCCs‚Äù). This is a pre-signed copy of this document which you may download, execute on your side, and return to DPA@unity3d.com.
