Personal data, as defined in the Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act (‚Äú
PIPEDA
‚Äù) will be collected, stored, used, and/or processed by the Zendesk Group in accordance with the Zendesk Group‚Äôs obligations under PIPEDA.
